Online Doctor Appointment System API:s
[text within brackets means user input data] 


LOGIN	patient & doctor
authenticateUser()
	IN	arguments:
		• [email address /userName]
		• [password]
	OUT	response:
		• OK 	logged in
		• NOK	error message


PATIENT
patientOverview()
	IN	arguments:
		• userID	(UUID ?)
	OUT	response:
		• profile data
		• <appointment list>		(replaces viewAllAppointments() ??)

initiateAppointment()		(i.e. search for ~)
	IN	arguments:
		• userID
		• [doctor]
		• [location]
		• [problem/ailment]
	OUT	response:
		• OK	<suggestion list>
				- timeSlot
				- doctor
				- location
		• NOK	error message ??

requestAppointment()
	IN	arguments:
		• userID
		• doctor
		• timeSlot (date + time)
	OUT	response:
		• OK	confirmation
		• NOK	error message

viewAllAppointments()		(not needed if the appointment list is included in the patientOverview() end-point method )
	IN	arguments:
		• userID
	OUT	response:
		• <appointment list>
			- timeSLot
			- doctor
			- location
			- problem/ailment

giveFeedback()
	IN	arguments:
		• appointmentID
		• feedback
	OUT	response:
		• OK	confirmation
		• NOK	error message


DOCTOR
doctorOverview()			(renamed from viewProfile()…)
	IN	arguments:
		• userID
	OUT	response:
		• profile data

updateProfile()
	IN	arguments:
		• userID
		• (updated) profile data
	OUT	response:
		• OK	confirmation
		• NOK	error message

viewAllAppointmentRequests()
	IN	arguments:
		• doctorID
	OUT	response:
		• <appointment list>
			- timeSlot
			- patient
			- problem/ailment

viewAppointment()
	IN	arguments:
		• appointmentID
	OUT	response:
		• patient data
		• appointment data

confirmAppointmentRequest()
	IN	arguments:
		• appointmentID
	OUT	response:
		• OK	confirmation
		• OK	notification via email to patient
		• NOK	error message

updateAppointment()
	IN	arguments:
		• appointmentID
		• (updated) appointment data
	OUT	response:
		• OK	confirmation
		• OK	notification via email to patient
		• NOK	error message

viewAllAppointments()
	IN	arguments:
		• doctorID
	OUT	response:
		• <appointment list>
			- timeSlot
			- patient
			- problem/ailment
			- ??

viewFeedback()
	IN	arguments:
		• appointmentID
	OUT	response:
		• feedback data

generateReport()
	IN	arguments:
		• doctorID
		• date (month)
	OUT	response:
		• exported text-based file (pdf, xls)
		• exported graphical file (pdf, xls) ?
		

